     C*
TCH56C*
     CLR                   Z-ADD0         BOXALL
     CLR                   TIME           @@TIME
     CLR                   EXCPTHY
B1   CLR         *IN56     DOWEQ'0'
     CLR                   READ GDGWP151                 56
B2   CLR         *IN56     IFEQ '0'
     CLR                   ADD  IBMAIS    BOXALL
     CLR                   EXCPTMY
     CLR         *INOV     IFEQ '1'
     CLR                   EXCPTHY
     CLR                   SETOF                     OV
     CLR                   END
E2   CLR                   ENDIF
E1   CLR                   ENDDO
     CLR                   EXCPTTY
TCH56C*
     CLR                   EXCPTTO
